snippet.title: TUNIC - Developer Commentary Gameplay Demo
snippet.description:
Want to know the inside scoop on the TUNIC gameplay demo? Lead developer Andrew Shouldice and Finji Community Manager Harris Foster are here to walk you through this tight, tip-of-the-iceberg experience to introduce you to TUNIC.

Want to learn more? 

http://www.tunicgame.com/
https://discord.gg/finji
